rComments: You need to put the work in for PSY380. The readings are very dense and difficult. DBW was great, as he went through and explained all the papers (a literal blessing). He really wants his students to succeed-- and often stressed that if you don't understand a concept, you should ask questions as others may be struggling as well.

rComments: Amazing prof! Cares about his students. Takes time to answer questions and very willing to help students outside of class.   His class was difficult, but the content was really interesting. He adjusted the syllabus when he felt it was too difficult. Tests are specific so get ready to know details, but papers give real opportunity to do well!
